{"id":227054,"date":[{"year":1951,"month":5,"day":22}],"page":"3","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"","column":"","genre":"","count":"170","ytitle":"","mtitle":"杀人魔王黄匪阿关","ftitle":"","authors":[],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgaut>何基</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>何基　作</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入2号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1951\\05\\515m031301.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>㈠黄匪为蒋匪“游击队”惯匪，一贯在张桥一带，姦淫掳掠，敲诈勒索。</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入2号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1951\\05\\515m031302.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>㈡敌伪时期黄匪当过土匪头子，被他杀害有十多条人命，更曾惨无人道的炒吃人心。</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入2号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1951\\05\\515m031303.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>㈢黄匪在当地勾结敌伪，人民被他酷刑鞭打者无数。</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入2号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1951\\05\\515m031304.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>㈣黄匪依仗蒋匪势力，强奸过不少妇女；连他的岳母和女儿都被强姦。</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入2号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1951\\05\\515m031305.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>㈤解放后暗藏枪枝，企图待机暴动；暗中与匪特来往，进行反革命活动。</FONT>"}]}